
Requirements
============

 * GCC or other C/C++ compiler (support for C++14 required)
 * CMake
 * libpthreads (+ headers)
 * openssl (+ headers)
 * nlohmann's 'JSON for Modern C++' (https://github.com/nlohmann/json)


Build steps
===========

Extract a directory of your liking, then:

 $ mkdir build && cd build
 $ cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" ..
 $ make -j$(nproc)
 $ su
 # make install
